Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.73,0:00:09.81,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,The countless flowers,\Nenveloped in light...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.81,0:00:20.34,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,...gaze at tomorrow\Nwith unwavering eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.33,0:00:39.35,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Everyone wishes for me to be pure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:46.81,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,...but what can I bring\Nwith me to the frayed skies?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:53.90,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,What I've made my own\Nby breaking off flowers in bloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.90,0:00:59.53,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,All such sinful things...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.53,0:01:07.01,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Why did I stop making\Npromises with the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.01,0:01:14.28,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Because even if I try\Nto run far from all the pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.28,0:01:21.02,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,...a cold wind rustles\Nmy hair... Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.02,0:01:28.45,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Where can I ever find the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.46,0:01:38.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.51,0:01:39.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Big Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.54,0:01:43.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm Para-sama's pair! You can't\Njust tell me to team up with Alty now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.48,0:01:48.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Regarding Paraietta,\Nyou can easily be replaced.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.92,0:01:53.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,But no one can take\Nyour place as sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.02,0:01:57.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Ri Majon you inscribe will show\Nsome interesting results, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.58,0:01:59.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sisters?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.97,0:02:04.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is all for the sake of restoring\NChor Tempest to its former prestige.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.93,0:02:07.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,We simply can't\Nafford another fiasco.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.96,0:02:17.95,Titles,,90,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Sisters
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.80,0:02:19.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.57,0:02:23.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you're pushing away\Nsuch tiny bits of onion like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.17,0:02:26.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.88,0:02:30.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun, I didn't know\Nyou could be so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.31,0:02:34.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,So it really wasn't\Nsuch a big deal, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:39.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Saying how in love you were, but\Nthat's how much you care in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.06,0:02:42.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,— Mastiff! You're so sweet!\N— Killing other people...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.43,0:02:44.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kaim.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.03,0:02:49.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,What? Don't lash out just because\Nyour beloved Para-sama dumped you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.98,0:02:50.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:52.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Stop it right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.42,0:03:12.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Big Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.06,0:03:23.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, they're finally back to normal now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.67,0:03:27.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Really... Putting up with\Nsuch barbarous treatment...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.27,0:03:28.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm proud of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:33.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Morinas, I can't let you get away\Nwith using the word "barbarous."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.18,0:03:42.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey... That's unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.16,0:03:55.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Floe...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:58.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:03.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,My sister didn't mean to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.81,0:04:05.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,— It's just that...\N— It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.54,0:04:10.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because she's right\Nabout how much I care.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:16.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,I felt... like I was going\Nto burst inside, see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.59,0:04:19.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,I thought my heart\Nwas just going to stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:22.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.76,0:04:26.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,It didn't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:29.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,But the thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.30,0:04:36.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,I just don't want to ever\Nforget about that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.57,0:04:39.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.34,0:04:45.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Not to forget... about that night...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.11,0:04:47.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Big Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.30,0:05:03.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Come on, Floe. Left more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:06.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why's this boat leaking like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.35,0:05:10.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the Messis is quite pleased\Nhaving Simoun sibyllae help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.95,0:05:13.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable. I don't see how it flies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.98,0:05:14.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.41,0:05:16.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where's Kaim?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.46,0:05:20.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Still sulking.\NShe really is a pain in the butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.39,0:05:26.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.22,0:05:31.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kaim, about tomorrow's test flight...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.14,0:05:34.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,They've decided to send Aer\Nand myself to accompany you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.16,0:05:38.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't you even care, Para-sama?\NThat I'm not your pair anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.54,0:05:40.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Kaim.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:42.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't look at me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.62,0:05:43.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.69,0:05:45.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:47.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kaim...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.91,0:05:50.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,But it's not my fault either!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.53,0:05:53.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kaim!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:06:00.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,She seems so upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.60,0:06:03.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should've\Nat least accompanied her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:04.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't do any good for you to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.71,0:06:20.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Man, you busted it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:32.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Freezing! Jeez, we got rid of the rusty\Nwater, and now there's no hot water?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.09,0:06:33.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,What a bummer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.32,0:06:38.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Isn't that water cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.89,0:06:41.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,It won't wash off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.56,0:06:45.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,I scrub and scrub...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.53,0:06:48.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,But no matter how much...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.78,0:06:50.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,...it just won't wash off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.95,0:07:09.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's get some sleep now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.49,0:07:12.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone, aren't you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:15.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,You can come over to my bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.90,0:07:17.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.07,0:07:20.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be brave.\NAfter all, you're still little...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.11,0:07:22.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,The truth is you're\Nthe one who's scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.17,0:07:25.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,T-That's not true...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.09,0:07:45.65,Lyrics top,,0,0,0,,Proof that an eternal world exists...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:53.20,Lyrics top,,0,0,0,,...shall be revealed\Nby Tempus Spatium.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.73,0:08:01.91,Lyrics top,,0,0,0,,Rocking gently\Nuntil we awake tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:06.64,Lyrics top,,0,0,0,,...protected by our mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:01.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:03.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:59.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is the first time, isn't it?\NThat we've flown together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.63,0:10:01.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's called "praying to the skies."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:06.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Big Sister... How did\Nwe ever come to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:12.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,We used to always do things together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:19.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,— It was that night...\N— Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:31.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer, after them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.11,0:10:42.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer, the communication cable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:42.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.21,0:10:49.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.11,0:10:52.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.32,0:11:00.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kaim! Alty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.02,0:11:05.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why? Why aren't their prayers\Nbeing heard by the Simoun gem?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.18,0:11:10.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're in the clouds...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:12.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,I won't lose them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.02,0:11:17.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Big Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:18.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't call me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.36,0:11:21.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Big Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.41,0:11:23.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,I said stop calling me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:33.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was right after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.19,0:11:38.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,You were to blame after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.64,0:11:41.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Alty... It's all your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.46,0:11:45.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right... It was all...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:47.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was all because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:55.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,What could that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.99,0:12:47.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wow... it's as\Ndilapidated as the Messis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:49.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Still, what the heck is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.90,0:12:52.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's Shoukoku's aerial base.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.62,0:12:58.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,But who would've thought\Na base this size even existed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:13:02.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,They don't seem to have spotted us,\Neven though we're so close.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.61,0:13:04.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Shall we explore?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:10.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, it's risky. With the other Simoun's\Noddness, let's return to the Messis...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.02,0:13:14.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was useless from the start. Even\NDominüra should be able to see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.02,0:13:16.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,We may be sisters, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.70,0:13:24.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:26.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Alty?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.30,0:13:32.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll show Dominüra that it's\Nnot impossible for us to be a team.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.11,0:13:39.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me.\NAer and Kaim will wait in the Simouns.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:42.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,We'll approach at a slow\Npace and then move in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.93,0:13:44.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,If something happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.43,0:14:26.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,It looks deserted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:27.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:29.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.80,0:14:35.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,A broken searchlight...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.14,0:14:37.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,A base left unguarded...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.55,0:14:42.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,So we're suffering at the hands\Nof people like this, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.38,0:14:43.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.52,0:14:48.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,How can they even confront\Nour divine vessels in battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.42,0:14:51.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's not a matter\Nof who's more powerful...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.59,0:14:53.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do you think they're not afraid to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:57.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't think there's\Nanyone who isn't afraid to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:14:59.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then they must be strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:02.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm envious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.87,0:15:06.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Alty...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.04,0:15:15.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's no need to be\Nthe strong one all on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.65,0:15:20.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's all Alty's fault. That girl's always...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.98,0:15:24.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,...always getting in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:25.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:28.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why does she always...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:31.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,What happened\Nbetween you and Alty?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.19,0:15:37.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,You two have this really weird vibe...\NEven though you're sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.10,0:15:40.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's because we are sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.40,0:15:42.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,That night...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:55.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,That night, I was feeling vulnerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.15,0:15:59.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'd be going into my\Nfirst battle in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,0:16:03.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,And I was scared. I wanted\Nto scream. I wanted to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.83,0:16:06.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,At that moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.53,0:16:14.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,She took advantage of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.14,0:16:16.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,I couldn't say no to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.45,0:16:19.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,When Alty seduced me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.92,0:16:26.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't really get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.72,0:16:30.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't blame you.\NFor sisters, it's an abominable sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.89,0:16:32.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's not what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:36.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is it really a matter of who\Nwas right and who was wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.89,0:16:38.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,But of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.67,0:16:43.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't tell from just hearing this.\NMaybe you really did the seducing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.70,0:16:48.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Seduced her? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.02,0:17:08.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,I seduced her? That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.76,0:17:11.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,I couldn't have...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.42,0:17:12.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kaim?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.29,0:17:16.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've got to make sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.00,0:17:18.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've got to bring Alty back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:19.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Kaim!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.22,0:17:21.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kaim!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.11,0:17:31.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,When we were little,\NI was always a little crybaby...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.69,0:17:34.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,And whenever I cried...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.05,0:17:38.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,...Big Sister would\Nalways hold me close.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:44.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,And I became stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.23,0:17:56.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,What I'd like to go back to isn't that\Nnight but a warm, cozy afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:18:04.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,What I want isn't the hand that\Ntaught me sensations I'd never known.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.23,0:18:08.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's the gentle hand that\Nheld mine as we walked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.40,0:18:13.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,But... Big Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.62,0:18:18.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to become a man someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:21.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,So that next time,\NI can hold her close.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.66,0:18:24.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,To hold Big Sister tight...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:32.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Big Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.53,0:18:57.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Big Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.83,0:19:06.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Big Sister! Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.62,0:19:15.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Big Sister, what's the matter?\NYou don't have to worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.34,0:19:17.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because I'll catch you\Nand hold you close!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.01,0:19:27.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Big Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.89,0:19:33.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's not my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.41,0:19:55.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kaim, as soon as we land,\Nact as Aer's sagitta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.39,0:19:56.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kaim! Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:19:58.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.43,0:20:37.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Simoun gem was\Nunaffected by their prayers?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.77,0:20:43.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see... Have you ever heard\Nof that happening before?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.37,0:20:45.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, never.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.71,0:20:50.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,As for Shoukoku's aerial base,\Nwe can't very well ignore it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.85,0:20:54.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Apparently there's a new\Nclass of aircraft on that base.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.29,0:21:07.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,To become strong by being held...\NYou're wrong about that, Alty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.13,0:21:13.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's only when you've\Nboth become strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:15.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,...that you can truly\Nhold each other close.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.84,0:21:21.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer, is my sister all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:23.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was just a scrape.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.72,0:21:24.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.95,0:21:34.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, you never got\Nto hold Amuria close, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.98,0:21:38.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. It'll happen with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.70,0:21:47.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,The person you're\Nlooking at right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.53,0:21:52.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,...is someone who will never\Ngrow old, and it's you yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.38,0:21:56.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.21,0:22:34.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,The same taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.12,0:22:47.83,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,It is played by my wounds...\Nthe song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.83,0:22:52.07,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Let it ring out over\Nthe grieving universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.07,0:22:59.14,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Can we change tomorrow?\NDon't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.14,0:23:06.74,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,I want to let you know\Nhow my heart's overflowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.56,0:23:19.63,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,"I want to get closer to you."\N"I want to feel your pulse."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.63,0:23:24.80,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,I was too defiant,\Nand I took the long way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.80,0:23:28.78,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,The blue moon is swaying silently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.78,0:23:32.82,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,My true heart's desire is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.82,0:23:38.69,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,I can't reach you.\NMy tears of pain trickle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.69,0:23:44.23,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Soar away into the sky, song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.23,0:23:47.66,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Carrying my love that came too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.66,0:23:53.33,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,What can I do to change tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.33,0:23:59.56,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Just hold on to "now" the way it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.92,0:24:06.63,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.04,0:24:11.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril screams, losing her\Nhead over something Aer says.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.51,0:24:16.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time on Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.05,0:24:18.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Reason.
